Come_Hither.help: You can Deceive an enemy into believing his friends are not who they appear to be. If successful, the enemy will ignore you and attack his own allies. If you Deceive someone before they have noticed you, your presence will continue to be masked. You will not receive any Experience Points for foes defeated by a Deceived enemy. Recharge: Moderate
Come_Hither.targetHelp: You have been confused. You may attack an incorrect target.

Hellish_Bolts.help: You summon a wave of mire that sweeps away foes within its arc.
Hellish_Bolts.targetHelp: You summon a wave of mire that sweeps away foes within its arc.

Entrance.help: Entrance and renders a foe helpless, lost in his own mind and unable to defend himself.

Bitter_Ice_Blast.help: A slower yet more powerful version of Ice Blast, Bitter Ice Blast deals much more damage and can also reduce your enemy's Accuracy. Like other Ice Blast powers, Bitter Ice Blast can Slow a target's movement and attack speed. Damage: Superior, Recharge: Slow
Bitter_Ice_Blast.targetHelp: Your Accuracy, Attack rate and Running speed are reduced by the Bitter Ice Blast.

Glacier.help: You can freeze all foes around yourself in blocks of Glacial ice. The targets are frozen solid, helpless, and can be attacked. Even after the victims emerge, they remain chilled and their attack and movement speed is Slowed for a while. This power can only be cast near the ground. Recharge: Very Long
Glacier.targetHelp: You are frozen in a Glacier. Once free, your Attack Rate and Running speed will be reduced slightly for a while.

Fire_Cages.help: Immobilizes a group of foes in Fire Cages, dealing Fire damage over time. More resilient foes may require multiple Fire Cages to Immobilize. Fire Cages is slower and less damaging than Ring of Fire, but can capture multiple targets. Damage: Minor(DoT), Recharge: Moderate
Fire_Cages.shortHelp: Ranged (Targeted AoE), Minor DoT(Fire), Foe Immobilize
Fire_Cages.targetHelp: The Fire Cage is burning you and preventing you from moving.
